---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Newsletter from "../components/Newsletter.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
import PageHero from "../components/PageHero.astro";
import image4 from "../assets/image4.png";
import image5 from "../assets/image5.png";
---

<Layout>
  <Header />

  <PageHero
    label="CASE STUDIES"
    title="Taxes & Efficiency"
    subhead="Our achievements reflect the close collaboration between our expert teams and our esteemed clientele. We cultivate a workplace that champions peak performance and guarantees client satisfaction."
  />

  <article class="cs_article flow">
    <div class="cs_article_inner">
      <div class="cs_image_wrap">
        <img
          src={image4.src}
          alt="Laptop and coffee on desk"
          class="cs_image_main"
          width="800"
          height="480"
        />
        <div class="cs_image_meta">
          <div class="cs_meta_items_group">
            <div class="cs_meta_item">
              <span class="cs_meta_label">Case Name</span>
              <span class="cs_meta_value">Taxes &amp; Efficiency</span>
            </div>
            <div class="cs_meta_item">
              <span class="cs_meta_label">Category</span>
              <span class="cs_meta_value">Business</span>
            </div>
            <div class="cs_meta_item">
              <span class="cs_meta_label">Date</span>
              <span class="cs_meta_value">27th September 2025</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs_meta_cta">
            <Button
              text="Live Preview"
              paddingX="33px"
              paddingY="16px"
              bgColor="#ffcc4a"
              textColor="var(--color-black)"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="cs_section">
        <h2 class="cs_h2">Project Overview</h2>
        <p class="cs_body">
          Carrying out a major operational study allowed us to elevate data
          handling and streamline core tasks. By engaging each department
          thoroughly, we minimized wasted energy and promoted transparent
          communication. These changes empower the workforce to address key
          goals efficiently while boosting productivity. Advanced resources
          drive sustained innovation. Frequent reviews keep teams aligned with
          strategic objectives.
        </p>
        <ul class="cs_list">
          <li>
            It brings the right people together with all the right information
            and tools to get work done
          </li>
          <li>
            We provide operational efficiency, data security, and flexible scale
          </li>
          <li>
            Your best work, together in one package that works seamlessly from
            your computer
          </li>
          <li>
            Delivers the tools you need to save time improve field performance
            always
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="cs_section">
        <h2 class="cs_h2">Storyboard</h2>
        <p class="cs_body">
          Completely synergize resource taxing relationships via premier niche
          markets. Professionally cultivate one-to-one customer service with
          robust ideas. Dynamically innovate resource-leveling customer service
          for state of the art customer service. Objectively innovate empowered
          manufactured products whereas parallel platforms. Holistically
          predominate extensible testing procedures for reliable supply chains.
        </p>
        <p class="cs_body">
          Proactively envisioned multimedia based expertise and cross-media
          growth strategies. Seamlessly visualize quality intellectual capital
          without superior collaboration and idea-sharing. Holistically
          pontificate installed base portals after maintainable products
          completely pursue scalable customer service.
        </p>
        <img
          src={image5.src}
          alt="Two colleagues working together"
          class="cs_image_inline"
          width="600"
          height="400"
        />
      </section>

      <section class="cs_section">
        <h2 class="cs_h2">Project result</h2>
        <p class="cs_body">
          Leverage agile frameworks to provide a robust synopsis for high level
          overviews. Iterative approaches to corporate strategy foster
          collaborative thinking to further the overall value proposition.
          Organically grow the holistic world view of disruptive innovation via
          workplace diversity and empowerment.
        </p>
        <p class="cs_body">
          Bring to the table win-win survival strategies to ensure proactive
          domination. At the end of the day, going forward, a new normal that
          has evolved from generation X is on the runway heading towards a
          streamlined cloud solution. User generated content in real-time will
          have multiple touchpoints for offshoring.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>

  <Newsletter />
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Artikel */
  .cs_article {
    --flow-space: var(--space-2xl);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-l) var(--space-3xl);
  }
  .flow > * + * {
    margin-top: var(--flow-space, var(--space-m));
  }

  .cs_article_inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    --flow-space: var(--space-2xl);
  }
  .cs_article_inner > * + * {
    margin-top: var(--flow-space);
  }

  /* Sektioner og inline-billede centreres til 709px */
  .cs_section,
  .cs_image_inline {
    max-width: 709px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* Hovedbillede med meta-bar */
  .cs_image_wrap {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: calc(167px * 0.75);
  }

  .cs_image_main {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
    aspect-ratio: 1200 / 451;
    background: var(--color-gray);
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .cs_image_meta {
    background: var(--color-black);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 28px 60px;
    width: min(1028px, 90%);
    box-sizing: border-box;
    border-radius: 30px;
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }

  .cs_meta_items_group {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 550px;
  }

  .cs_meta_item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    --flow-space: var(--space-3xs);
  }
  .cs_meta_item > * + * {
    margin-top: var(--flow-space);
  }

  .cs_meta_label {
    font-family: "Lato";
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-white);
    line-height: 148%;
  }

  .cs_meta_value {
    font-family: "Lato";
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 148%;
  }

  .cs_meta_cta {
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  /* Sektioner */
  .cs_section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    --flow-space: var(--space-m);
  }
  .cs_section > * + * {
    margin-top: var(--flow-space);
  }

  .cs_h2 {
    font-family: "Cabin Variable";
    font-size: var(--step-2);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 116%;
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cs_body {
    font-family: "Lato";
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 160%;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cs_list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: var(--space-m);
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    --flow-space: var(--space-xs);
  }
  .cs_list > * + * {
    margin-top: var(--flow-space);
  }

  .cs_list li {
    font-family: "Lato";
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 160%;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .cs_image_inline {
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: block;
    aspect-ratio: 709 / 365;
    background: var(--color-gray);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .cs_image_wrap {
      padding-bottom: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .cs_image_main {
      border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
    }

    .cs_image_meta {
      position: static;
      transform: none;
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px;
      padding: var(--space-m) var(--space-l);
      gap: var(--space-m);
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .cs_meta_items_group {
      gap: var(--space-l);
      max-width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .cs_image_meta {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: var(--space-s);
    }

    .cs_meta_items_group {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: var(--space-xs);
    }

    .cs_meta_cta {
      margin-left: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
